quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,195,"Nuko Nyagasani wabo abakirira ubusabe (agira ati) \"Mu by’ukuri, jye sinagira impfabusa igikorwa cyakozwe n’umwe muri mwe, yaba uw’igitsina gabo cyangwa uw’igitsina gore, kuko mukomokanaho (murareshya mu guhemberwa ibyo mukora). Bityo babandi bimutse bakanameneshwa mu ngo zabo, bagatotezwa bazira kugana inzira yanjye, bakarwana, bakanicwa, rwose nzabababarira ibyaha byabo nanabinjize mu busitani (Ijuru) butembamo imigezi. Ibyo ni ibihembo biturutse kwa Allah, kandi kwa Allah ni ho hari ibihembo byiza"
  3,196,Ntuzashukwe n’umudendezo abahakanye bafite ku isi
  3,197,"Ni umunezero w’akanya gato, hanyuma ubuturo bwabo bukaba mu muriro wa Jahanamu kandi ni yo buturo bubi"
  3,198,"Ariko babandi batinye Nyagasani wabo, bazagororerwa ubusitani butembamo imigezi (mu ijuru), bazabubamo ubuziraherezo. Bizaba ari izimano rivuye kwa Allah, kandi ibiri kwa Allah ni byo byiza ku bakora neza"
  3,199,"Mu by’ukuri, mu bahawe ibitabo harimo abemera Allah n’ibyomwa- hishuriwe (Qur’an) ndetsen’ibyo bahishuriwe bibombarika (Tawurati imbere ya n’Ivanjili); Allah. Ntibagurana amagambo ya Allah igiciro gito; abo bazahabwa ingororano zabo kwa Nyagasani wabo. Kandi mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubanguka mu ibarura"
  3,200,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwihangane munihanganishanye, kandi mushikame (ku rugamba), ndetse mutinye Allah kugira ngo mukiranuke"